    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home where its potential can truly shine. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone who loves a hands-on restoration project or needs a reliable source of parts. It's an affordable opportunity to roll up your sleeves and bring a classic back to life!",
